                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-172" type="given" value="RICHARD CALVERT"></interp>RICHARD CALVERT SHEPPARD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a woollen-cloth manufacturer, and live in Great Scotland-yard. On the 13th of April, I was in Buck<lb></lb>lersbury on business—I left my chaise in the care of a boy, who left it—when I came out I found a crowd gathered—this is my coat.</p>
